'''Leo Stadium''' is a three-sided [[List of football stadiums in Thailand|football stadium]] in [[Thanyaburi District|Thanyaburi]], [[Pathum Thani Province|Pathum Thani]], [[Thailand]], holding 16,014  spectators. It is the home of [[BG Pathum United F.C.|BG Pathum United]] of the [[Thai League 1]]. Since opened, the ground has been installed with high-quality [[Artificial turf|artificial surface]]. However, from the season 2018 onward the stadium will be replaced with real [[grass]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.buaksib.com/%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%9E%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%B2-%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3-2017-11-02/|title=อัพเดทความคืบหน้า การปรับปรุงพื้นสนาม ลีโอ สเตเดี้ยม รับซีซั่น 2018|work=}}</ref>
