'''Tebwaia Baikawa''' (born 16 September 1983), is a retired [[Kiribati|I-Kiribati]] [[Association football|footballer]] who played as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]].
==International career== Baikawa represented Kiribati at the [[Men's football at the 2003 South Pacific Games|2003 Pacific Games]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/kiri-recintlp.html |title=Appearances and Goals for Kiribati National Team |accessdate=26 April 2018 |work=[[Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation]]}}</ref>
